-analysis-determines-that-water-once-flowed-on-asteroid-ryugu2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Sep 2025 11:42:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/09/isotopic-analysis-determines-that-water-once-flowed-on-asteroid-ryugu</guid></item><item><title>金属纳米催化剂：催化过程中真正发生了什么</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/09/metallic-nanocatalysts-what-really-happens-during-catalysis</link><description>通过在Desy的纳米舞中使用贝西II上的光谱显微镜和微观分析的组合，团队对催化过程中纳米催化剂的化学行为有了新的见解。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/metallic-nanocatalysts-what-really-happens-during-catalysis.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Sep 2025 11:27:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/09/metallic-nanocatalysts-what-really-happens-during-catalysis</guid></item><item><title>新技术将绘画变成全息图，使艺术栩栩如生</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/09/new-technology-turns-paintings-into-holograms-bringing-art-to-life</link><description>艺术家一直在寻找创造和表达自己的新方法。增长的趋势是使用多种透明材料（例如有机玻璃）来创建具有真实深度的绘画，将二维图像转化为三维幻觉，使人感觉更现实和栩栩如生。但是，这些分层的作品是否可以使其更加身临其境？ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-technology-turns-paintings-into-holograms-bringing-art-to-life.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Sep 2025 11:12:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/09/new-technology-turns-paintings-into-holograms-bringing-art-to-life</guid></item></channel></rss>